CatDescriptText: A calander from Green Bag Cement hangs on the wall displaying the months of December 1945, through February 1946.  A can of Tinner's Red paint is stored on a low shelf, and there is a radio near a staircase in the back of the room.
TitMainTitle: Newly built wooden rowboat resting on the floor of a workshop
